<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">انظر:</span> <span class="c2">((جامع الأصول)</span>) <span class="c2">(٢/٧١٦)</span> .<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>